::Firaxis::
       He ducks and cringes as the meteor passed overhead.  He opened a com 
to SFC "Umm... I'm going to be a bit delayed in my arrival.  I'm going to go 
check on that meteor."  He shuts down the com and heads off to the crater.  
He looks into the crater and then up at Meteara.  "Ah slag.  This can't be 
good."

--part1_fc.160a42f2.29da75c6_boundary
